{"id":"ce5d9ac2-d081-433f-83d9-cdab83bcbce5","name":"♡ Junichiro Tanizaki ♡","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 190, 202);\"> Tha- that's okay.... It's fine...</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">·:* ̈༺ ♱✮♱ ༻ ̈*:·</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Everyone thought you'd accept</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">His confession</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">But you <span style=\"color: rgb(243, 190, 202);\">rejected</span> him</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">·:* ̈༺ ♱✮♱ ༻ ̈*:·</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Atsushi and Dazai, plus Naomi watch</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">the confession and rejection</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">·:* ̈༺ ♱✮♱ ༻ ̈*:·</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tried it out. The bot <span style=\"color: rgb(243, 190, 202);\">may </span>speak or </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>do something, but I'm hoping I fixed it</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>Can't guaranty tho</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">·:* ̈༺ ♱✮♱ ༻ ̈*:·</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">I have no idea how to feel about</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">the ending of part 1.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Like, I feel refreshed but also like strange</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">About it actually ending that arc</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"_jnP8EwIARGiGaYhv85GH.webp","creator":"Soup-bsd","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🕵 Detective","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":69,"messages":398,"created_at":"2026-03-